    <title>CKAN: Ticket #35: IP Address for non-logged in users is always 127.0.0.1 when deployed behind a proxy (e.g. on ckan.net)</title>
    <link>http://localhost/ticket/35</link>
    <description>&lt;p&gt;
When IP address is used to identify non-logged in users (for example on create and editing of packages) it is always 127.0.0.1 when using a reverse proxy (standard deployment configuration on a production machine and used e.g. on &lt;a class="ext-link" href="http://www.ckan.net"&gt;&lt;span class="icon"&gt;â€‹&lt;/span&gt;http://www.ckan.net&lt;/a&gt;).
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
This could be corrected by using HTTP_X_FORWARDED_FOR when available.
&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
